replies.body:
Honestly?  They just need to remove the most degenerate forms of additional damage that were added to the game.

The Big List
AD/AP given at level 1 from just picking Dom/Sorc/Insp+either
%arpen items giving too much free arpen
{{summoner:14}} 
Every single keystone; yes, even Guardian
{{item:3147}} 
{{item:3095}} 
New and reworked champions that do nothing but instagib.

Every facet of this game is now objectively awful because of these.  I've never seen Riot so desperate to lose money.
